#: etc/options.php:58
msgid ""
"The scope defines the navigation scope of this web application's "
"application context. It restricts what web pages can be viewed while the "
"manifest is applied. If the user navigates outside the scope, it reverts to "
"a normal web page inside a browser tab or window."
msgstr ""

